# Codex/Claude project config is tracked; machine-local CLI config is not.
# .claude/settings.json is tracked codegen; settings.local.json is per-machine
# (worktree-init.mjs writes GIT_DIR/GIT_WORK_TREE into it). The repo's *.local
# rule does NOT match "settings.local.json" (it ends in .json), so name it.
.agents/*
!.agents/
!.agents/hooks.json
.codex/*
!.codex/hooks.json
.claude/settings.local.json

# AI 画像生成ツール (nanobanana) の出力スクラッチ — アイコンは icons/ に採用済み
nanobanana-output/

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Logs
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Environment / secrets — NEVER commit API keys
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.local
secrets.json
*.key

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Visual-feedback inbox (a future local daemon writes here)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.ai-inbox/
# The daemon's real inbox + the chrome.downloads FILE fallback use the
# dot-less "ai-inbox" name; ignore it too if it ever lands inside the repo.
ai-inbox/

